impulse,"## 2004

A Winamp skin I designed to showcase the new freeform skin design capabilities introduced with Winamp 5. This was a collaboration with R. Peter Clark who coded the interactions.

[Download.wal](https://kepano.s3.amazonaws.com/impulse.wal)

See [[rusty-heaven|Rusty Heaven]] and [[devastate|devASTATE]] for examples of Winamp 2 skins, which had strict limitations on design.

![Devastate skin](https://stephango.com/assets/impulse.jpg)
