piano,"I am learning to play piano and made this cheat sheet to help me learn scales. [Watch this video](https://x.com/kepano/status/1826291265786503525) to see how you can use the printable version with your piano.

## Interactive scales

Click the name of a scale or note to hear it play. You can change the root note, and use the number row on your keyboard to play notes and chords.

Unmute your device to play sounds on this page.

blues

harmonic

melodic minor

natural minor

major

