flexo,"My dog Flexo. His name was inspired by *flexography*. It appropriately happens to be the name of [Bender’s twin](https://futurama.fandom.com/wiki/Flexo) from Futurama. He also deserves credit for inspiring the name of my color scheme [[flexoki|Flexoki]].

![Flexo](https://stephango.com/assets/flexo.jpg)
